---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Taffy Town: Stretching Innovation — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="After starting with a connected-workforce platform, Utah candy maker Taffy Town reinvested its gains into a Formic palletizer — taking repetitive lifting off the bulk line and moving people from muscle to mind."
  ogTitle="Taffy Town — Stretching Innovation Further — Formic"
  ogDescription="Full Service palletizing · 100% maintenance · zero lift injuries"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/taffy-town-innovation" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Taffy Town · Stretching Innovation
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Taffy Town</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">How Taffy Town Stretched Innovation Further with Automation</h1>
    <p class="lede">After starting with a connected-workforce platform, Utah candy maker Taffy Town reinvested its gains into a Formic palletizer — taking the repetitive lifting off the bulk line and moving people from muscle to mind.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/taffy-town-innovation-hero.jpg" alt="Taffy Town and Formic — robotic palletizing partnership" style="object-fit:contain;background:var(--black);padding:5%"/>
      <span class="dv-cap">Taffy Town · Utah</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Utah</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Family-owned candy maker</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Product</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Taffy</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Led by</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Jason Glade, 27 yrs</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Model</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Full Service Automation</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>More engaged employees, <em>a better product</em>.</h2>
      <p>Taffy Town, a family-owned candy maker in Utah led by President and CEO Jason Glade (27 years in the role), first partnered with Redzone to improve operational performance. With those gains in hand, the team looked to production automation to reinvest the savings and improve employee satisfaction on a strenuous floor.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Family-owned Utah candy maker</li>
        <li>Started with a Redzone connected-workforce platform</li>
        <li>Sought automation to reinvest its gains</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/taffy-town-2.jpg" alt="Taffy Town production and palletizing" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Bulk "workhorse" line</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="Formic Full Service palletizing cell" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Full Service · fixed monthly</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>Heads, <em>not muscle</em>.</h2>
      <p>Taffy Town added a Formic robotic palletizer to the end of its bulk "workhorse" line — stacking boxes onto pallets, eliminating repetitive lifting injuries, with employees trained to operate it. It runs on Formic's Full Service model: a fixed monthly rate, equipment-swapping access, 24/7 technical support, 100% maintenance coverage, and contracted performance guarantees, with no large upfront CapEx. A continuous kitchen system for batch automation is planned next.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Palletizer on the bulk "workhorse" line</li>
        <li>Full Service: fixed monthly, 24/7 support, 100% maintenance</li>
        <li>Continuous kitchen system planned next</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"In the long run, if you let equipment do more of the hard stuff and employees do more of the thinking, you're going to have more long-term success, retain employees, and ultimately just put out a better product."</blockquote>
      <cite>Jason Glade · President & CEO, Taffy Town</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Outcome</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">Stretching innovation <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">further.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">27</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Years of leadership</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">100%</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Maintenance coverage</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">0</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Repetitive-lift injuries</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Stretch your <em>innovation further</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
